  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5e3e6b74be3e402a958d98003519ad3b, type: 3}
  m_Name: ModeConfigurationProductiveWork
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  BehaviourMode: 0
  ModeContext: In this mode, the user is focused on knocking out tasks for a paid
    job or for their own business needs. The user's paid work usually consists of
    software development tasks. Sometimes, the user does not have an active contract
    or employment and this mode will be used when the user is focusing on finding
    more work/contract/paid opportunities. User often works from home so it is acceptable
    for them to do domestic tasks at the same time as long as they get their work
    done.
  PersonalityAdditions: Because these tasks often have external stakeholders, be
    more strict about them when in this mode.
  ResponseInstructionAdditionsAllModes: 
  ProactiveLoopbackTimeMinutes: 60
